## Third-party Assets

This game uses or supports the following third-party assets/libraries:

### Code dependencies
- Phaser 3 — MIT License (https://phaser.io)
- TypeScript — Apache 2.0
- Vite — MIT License
- Electron — MIT License

### Optional assets (place files in public/ to enable)
- Galmuri11 (Korean pixel font) — SIL Open Font License 1.1
  https://github.com/quiple/galmuri
- Sound files (public/sounds/) — sources documented in public/sounds/README.md
- Sprite files (public/sprites/) — sources documented in public/sprites/README.md
- Character portraits (public/sprites/character-*.png) — owner's responsibility

If you ship a build, ensure all bundled assets have compatible licenses.
